 ##-------------------------------------------------- The kali linux in Windows 10 ---------------------------------------------##
 INSTALL GUI

⚙️ sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y

⚙️ sudo apt install kali-desktop-xfce -y

XRDP

⚙️ sudo apt install xrdp -y

⚙️ sudo service xrdp start

⚙️ ip address
& Copy the ip address

# Open Remote Desktop Connection app and paste the link
# write the credential and the process is complete.

